api_list.name: /feedback
api_list.description:
This endpoint enables you to send us feedback about specific LO.

> Please note that `url` is required in the body but `comment` and `request_id` are optional.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://learning-objects-v2.p.rapidapi.com/feedback"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "learning-objects-v2.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
